<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7269075">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7269075/" class="title-link">中华书局《近代史料笔记丛刊》竟整理的如此草率</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7269075"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ultra312/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1523814-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ultra312/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">ultra312</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-22"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-22 10:35:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7269075_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     本人一直以为中华书局算得上中国古籍整理的老大，所出书大多还是优于上海古籍的。没想到这套《近代史料笔记丛刊》竟如此大跌眼镜。这套书实际上是复刻四川人民的《近代稗海》。但是既然是古籍整理而非影印，总应该根据原始版本重新校点，可是这套书实际上就是《近代稗海》的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7269075_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7269075_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
